metadata.name: Old Man Jenkins
metadata.description:
Looking for something unique and special to add to your NFT collection?

Look no further than Old Man Jenkins. This piece is a one-of-a-kind work of art that has been painted on canvas paper using watercolors and then further manipulated in adobe fresco on the ipad. It's a true work of art that any collector would be proud to own.

But don't wait too long! Prices will only rise as the artist continues to create new pieces for the collection. So invest now and help take this collection further!
